{"tid":253252,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"同髮型師吹水係一種享受","createTime":"2017-05-22T09:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T09:34:41.000Z","uid":81722,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"367337b3764f08f96af419f80b894927e962e520","tid":253252,"uid":81722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"當然唔係個個都咁健談<br />\n但我由細到大遇到既髮型師都有好多人生格言<br />\n細個會哄你開心 叫你努力讀書<br />\n大個就討論好多人生觀 比建議你點做人<br />\n所以搵髮型師 搵到個幾傾得計 講野幾理性既<br />\n都算係人生一大福份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d187e65aaf08aa1d2b2ac2aff8baad24da7b8b57","tid":253252,"uid":81552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"但洗頭個陣其實唔太想應，同埋有時趕時間就會有啲老尷⋯"},{"pid":"b0b5d35188a32771808748c3ff6cb165305704ed","tid":253252,"uid":642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"貴價果d好多串柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d860a9b2912e3d317a01cc1c1c523f87ad03a65","tid":253252,"uid":81722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但洗頭個陣其實唔太想應，同埋有時趕時間就會有啲老尷⋯</blockquote><br />\n我剪開個間 洗頭還洗頭 剪髮還剪髮 所以未試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26db198b6782e53116f8462f06da3cd26fdce02e","tid":253252,"uid":81722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貴價果d好多串柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d係串 但好多都好好態度<br />\n唔係點哄你做忠誠顧客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef97b8bec44599b43d2b42f92f4c3333b24c8a5","tid":253252,"uid":54667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:12:02.000Z","msg":"毒撚表示如果個髮型師係咁R水吹<br />\n一定冇下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5d199e191fcfb51d066a2751746bf13c8ee2c2","tid":253252,"uid":29131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"我係唔會應佢地 專心剪我個頭好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e86f0b0f8cd4af1c92699e747c66954e4e663de","tid":253252,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:15:54.000Z","msg":"通常佢地會同你吹水睇你咩性格<br />\n繼而剪個咩頭比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個客健談好傾既話都會肯用心剪d"},{"pid":"ebf9e69bdc41a12f70d6dcc9414270ecb4f83425","tid":253252,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貴價果d好多串柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d係串 但好多都好好態度<br />\n唔係點哄你做忠誠顧客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個頭剪成點先係重點, 剪得唔好, 你態度幾好都冇用"},{"pid":"25c1f3824ce202610b89dae05d7ceb773d68771d","tid":253252,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"唔知點解好多時初期開頭先多野講<br />\n不過去到後期越來越少野傾or dead air"},{"pid":"d577d95a55777baab7986906b8ecdcec0abdb835","tid":253252,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係唔會應佢地 專心剪我個頭好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/22/173401_832d1d3fc189069f2914bacb97f93a6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2F173401_832d1d3fc189069f2914bacb97f93a6f.jpg&h=d0c59fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n專心啲剪啦，咪撚剪柒我個頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}